    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of an order containing cellulose-eating insects, the social system of which shows remarkable parallels with those of ants and bees, although it has evolved independently.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
